title=Preferences pane  saving to a stack or text file.
topics=<p>Key Topics Covered in this Tutorial:</p>\n<p>-&#9;A walk through the Preferences Pane sample project</p>\n<p>-&#9;How to view the scripts</p>\n<p>-&#9;Editing grouped objects</p>\n<p>-&#9;A look at two simple ways of saving data</p>